issue.title: [ORT Mobile] Some updates to iOS/Android build settings

repository.name: onnxruntime
repository.description: ONNX Runtime: cross-platform, high performance ML inferencing and training accelerator

issue.body:
**Description**: Some updates to iOS/Android build settings
- Enable code signing for iOS in build directly
- Make check binary size for Android minimal build optional
- Move Android test in build.py to a separated function
- Add build_java options to Android CI

**Motivation and Context**
- Some user may want to sign the iOS binary directly in build
- Check binary size may cause test failure for minimal build if some ops are included (technically it's not a failure, nut will cause user confusion)
- Add build_java can detect issues such as https://github.com/microsoft/onnxruntime/issues/4976
